data.description: The Dorsey-Riverbend community is located in the heart of Ft Lauderdale, FL.  This COZY duplex features 2 beds / 1 bath per unit, updated kitchen cabinets, new water heater, 3yr old roof and recessed lighting.  The long porch allows for relaxation.  Spacious back yard would be great for entertaining; land has potential for additional units.  Unit 2 is being leased on a month-to-month basis for $1200 mo.  Rent can easily go for $1850 per unit or more.  Each unit has their own electrical meter, water bill and lawn care is currently included in the rent.  Pets are allowed, and NO HOA!  Downtown Ft Lauderdale is filled with amazing activities i.e., museums, art galleries, performing arts centers and theaters.  It’s minutes from Ft Lauderdale beaches, the train station and Highway I-95.
